#, python-brace-format
msgctxt "Command Line Help"
msgid ""
"Location of Batteryless SRAM data in ROM (e.g. 0xFC0000); only with "
"“{dmg_savetype_batteryless}” or “{agb_savetype_batteryless}”)"
msgstr ""
"ROM 中无电池 SRAM 数据的位置（例如 0xFC0000）；"
"仅与“{dmg_savetype_batteryless}”或“{agb_savetype_batteryless}”一起使用"

